{
  "stem": "766.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And once, one brought-- she got, from somebody, stockings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they gave me a pair of stockings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't put them on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because first of all, she'd be asking where from I have stockings?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't have with what to hold them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I didn't put them on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I got, I remember, a-- a-- an act of spasm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody gave me something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A girl, you understand?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What, I am supposed to help her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so this was an emotional-- some-- some public human relation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I get a pair of stockings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't put them on because I was afraid of her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because if I wear, they say, who gave it to me?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they-- so the German gave her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it-- it's better not, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this, I just want to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now when it came the time that probably the Russian approached, they liquidated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They packed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When was that?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- we came over there in-- in February, sometimes in the beginning of February, end of January.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was winter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they came different transport from others on the way to-- to join and go together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So came a doctor from another camp with a transport and said to me, make your people go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you say you are sick, they shoot them out right away, what they do with her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I have to tell the men that were sick, but how can I talk?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is a German, always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't talk Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I cannot tell them in German, this message.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But somehow, I managed to tell them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what is-- Some said, shoot or not shoot, I can't go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let me shoot, then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't volunteer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was another.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
